        dc:description           "Figures 3 - 6. Phyllidiella zeylanica, four specimens. Upper row (A) showing the dorsal pattern and lower row (B) illustrating their ventral sides 3 Hurghada, April 2009, S. Kahlbrock 4 Abu Kafan, 14 July 2015, S. Kahlbrock SK  13 5 near Hurghada, 2014, S. Kahlbrock 6 Hurghada, April 2015, S. Kahlbrock." , "Plates 4 - 8. Phyllidiella zeylanica, variations in dorsal pattern 4 Hurghada, April 2009 5 Abu Kafan, 14 July 2015, SK  13 6 - 8 three individuals not collected, near Hurghada (all photographs S. Kahlbrock)." ;
